{"tid":275443,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【旺角騷亂】警司指當日磚頭「好似落雨咁」","createTime":"2017-06-08T04:43:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-08T06:27:52.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"21c44caf51bfb8c01ea1bdbf24651a61c185d258","tid":275443,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T04:43:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170608/large/1496896093_768d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170608%2Flarge%2F1496896093_768d.jpg&h=a7555c86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去年大年初二凌晨旺角發生的騷亂，事後多人被控以暴動罪，其中涉及9名男子的案件今續審。案發時為總督察的現任警司陳偉基今出庭作供，指當日清晨5時他於豉油街警方防線，他形容當日示威者掟磚「好似落雨咁」，期間他頭、手中磚，左後腦須縫4針、左手無名指骨折，被評為1%永久傷殘，獲放8日病假。<br />\n<br />\n陳偉基指，案發時他看到有便衣同事欲拘捕一名青年但失敗，他上前協助將青年拘捕，該青年為首被告。陳相信因示威者見有人被捕故加密向警方掟磚，他左後腦、左耳上方被掟中，2至3秒後再有磚掟向他，他成功擋開。他形容當時頭中磚後有1至2秒「暈一暈」。<br />\n<br />\n陳繼續在現場觀察，看到前面有4名示威者在掟磚，其中3人是年輕人，另1人約60多歲，他警告4人：「唔好再掟啦，再掟拉你」，但他們未有理會，陳決定反守為攻拘捕他們，但3名年輕人跑得快逃脫，年長的那個跑得慢，陳與兩警員將對方拘捕，事後證實為第六被告。<br />\n<br />\n陳又指，警長黃樂安在控制早前被捕的首被告時被磚掟中，他看到黃當時「塊面好多血，好似無意識」，陳不斷問黃問題以保持他意識。<br />\n現時受審的9名被告順序為莫嘉濤（18歲）、鍾志華（31歲）、何錦森(38歲)、霍廷昊（24歲）、陳和祥（71歲）、鄧敬宗（27歲）、李卓軒（20歲）、林永旺（22歲）、葉梓豐（18歲）。"},{"pid":"ba9dde12f43443f831bec5d6295ab44e4ad62b6c","tid":275443,"uid":46644,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T04:44:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fe93d504dfef78d1dc6c14e3fd64eaa6c64b8fb8","tid":275443,"uid":31990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T04:44:48.000Z","msg":"d磚頭落雨咁又揼唔撚死你既?<br />\n<br />\n講大話?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ac1fb974ed2ca39a4eb6c09e335933f4c496da7","tid":275443,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T04:48:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>應該捉晒班暴徒去秦國坐終身</blockquote><br />\n呢排做返五毛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"012f1623ddfd2b293ee832604d349ee2668d3716","tid":275443,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T04:52:28.000Z","msg":"又話有個毀左容，唔推佢出黎大做文章既?"},{"pid":"99af2412105b30bd95df0876330270ccba207225","tid":275443,"uid":50533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T04:57:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"da327007b112896510d744361a4171b55978f003","tid":275443,"uid":49955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T05:34:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>希望重判班暴徒</blockquote><br />\nANGGER<br />\n速龍隊起碼判廿年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12224e45ad531ddbecc43d53a3eca46b21bde999","tid":275443,"uid":64966,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T05:36:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3oEjHTpdpGo1vGQRby/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3oEjHTpdpGo1vGQRby%2Fgiphy.gif&h=81614293&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3o7TKyRvIBycoKY8so/source.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3o7TKyRvIBycoKY8so%2Fsource.gif&h=c6e30b32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.giphy.com/26FPsF6AnUBwnqdos.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.giphy.com%2F26FPsF6AnUBwnqdos.gif&h=f7613e79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/26FPnpatcd94T0JLW/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F26FPnpatcd94T0JLW%2Fgiphy.gif&h=b585f810&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/5KEXNDz3wuac/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F5KEXNDz3wuac%2Fgiphy.gif&h=3743800e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/7aPsXPUuzFrJ6/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.gip